      },
      "message": "Hello!  Thanks for taking my call.  I'm ringing on behalf of a client who needs a removal quote.  They're moving from a two-bed flat in N1 7AA to a two-bed property in SW11 3RX on the first of August twenty twenty-six.  The origin is second floor with no lift,  parking about twenty meters away.  The destination is ground floor with parking about five meters away,  and there's a reservable bay available.\n \nThe inventory includes two double beds that need disassembly,  one three-seat sofa, two wardrobes that also need disassembly,  a dining table with chairs,  thirty-five boxes, and an upright piano.  They'll need disassembly service and insurance as well.  Can you give me an itemised quote for this move?",
