    {
      "role": "user",
      "agent_metadata": null,
      "message": "Alright, let's get you sorted.  For a two-bed move like this,  you're looking at around \u00a31, 900 to \u00a32,200.  Now, considering the second-floor situation with no lift,  there's a stairs fee of \u00a3120.  Plus, there's a fuel surcharge of \u00a380.  Since you're asking for a weekend slot,  there's a premium slot fee of \u00a3150.  Disassembly and insurance are all included,  mate.  I can only hold this price today,  so if you're ready to book,  we can lock it in.  How does that sound?",
      "multivoice_message": null,
      "tool_calls": [],
