    {
      "role": "user",
      "agent_metadata": null,
      "message": "Alright, my apologies, you're right, August 1st, twenty twenty-six is a Friday, so that's a weekday. No premium slot fee then.\n \nSo, for everything you've laid out \u2013 the two-bed flat, the disassembly, the piano, the stairs at origin, the parking situation, all the boxes, and the insurance \u2013 the total price for that move is \u00a32,100. That includes the fuel, the stairs fee, the labour, the truck, all the materials we'll need, and your insurance. It's all in there, mate.\n \nThat's a solid price for a comprehensive service like this. I can only hold that figure for you today. What do you say? Shall we get you booked in?",
