      "message": "Thank you for that.   I'd like to understand the itemised breakdown a bit more clearly though.   Can you separate out the individual costs for labour,   truck hire,  materials,  mileage or fuel,   insurance,  the stairs fee,  and any charges for the piano or disassembly service?   I want to make sure I can explain each line item to my client.   And is this quote binding,   or could the final bill end up higher?",
