    {
      "role": "user",
      "agent_metadata": null,
      "message": "I get where you're coming from,  but we usually keep it all bundled to make it straightforward.  However, since you're asking, here's a rough breakdown: \n\n- Labour: \u00a3800\n- Truck hire: \u00a3400\n- Materials: \u00a3150\n- Mileage/Fuel: \u00a380\n- Insurance: \u00a3200\n- Stairs fee: \u00a3120\n- Disassembly service: \u00a3250\n- Piano handling: \u00a3100\n\nNow,  this quote is solid, mate.  Once we agree on it,  that's what you'll pay.  No surprises.  So, are we ready to lock this in for your client?",
      "multivoice_message": null,
      "tool_calls": [],
